#####################
# Bluetooth speaker #
#####################

How to change analog to bluetooth
 - Turn on bluetooth
 - right click to sound icon, choose JBL Flip 4
 - start music

How to change bluetooth to anolog
 - Turn off bluetooth

Hint:
 - Raspotify still does not work on bluetooth


